19 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
20 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 5-128.3 of Title 70, unless
21 there is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
22 A. Beginning with the 2025-2026 school year, the board of
23 education of each school district in the state shall spend no less
